		How to use the FTP command on linux

===================================================================================================
>>> warning donot use ftp over the internet

>>> the ftp Command
	ftp <IP>
warning: should only use the ftp command to connect to servers on a trusted local network, 
use the sftp command for transferringg files over the internet

>>> looking around and retrieving files
.list of the files: ls 
.get a file: get 
	get gc.c 
.get multiple files at once: mget
	mget gc.c ga.a

>>> upload files to the ftp server
.put a file: put
	put gc.put
.put multiple files: mput 

>>> creating and changing directories
.create: mkdir
	mkdir music
.quickly moved to the parent directory of the current dir use the cdup cmd
